{"tid":684333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉劈枱恐嚇法官　工人炒大狀","createTime":"2018-05-30T12:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T12:46:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"546ed05bec09e37a8621c3f9757528a3840d2d9a","tid":684333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:27:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180530/20405519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180530%2F20405519&d=C5tuzVbK%2Fw0HjkR772TvCgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=f9e3cf09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180530%2F20405519&h=028ffc0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180530/20405519</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月30日 <br />\n<br />\n涉劈枱恐嚇法官　工人炒大狀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180530/large/30la2p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180530%2Flarge%2F30la2p04.jpg&h=fdc4ea15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■余祖林涉恐嚇法官，昨在區院提訊。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】裝修工余祖林涉於高等法院庭內亮刀兼劈枱，呼喝法官陳嘉信，其後高調自首，被控刑事恐嚇等罪。案件昨日在區域法院提訊時，余因不滿大狀不替他向法庭呼冤「炒大狀」，親自向法庭解釋只輕微打爛陳官的枱面，沒有恐嚇法官；他更抱拳跪地要求法庭批准他保釋，指「天（人）在做，人（天）在看！」但申請被拒。案件排期8月24日審訊。<br />\n<br />\n53歲的余被控刑事恐嚇、刑事損壞及藏有攻擊性武器3罪。他昨早以普通話向法官稱，曾多次告知法援委派的大律師他是冤枉的，但大律師沒代他呼冤，甚至申請精神科報告，害他被送小欖精神病治療中心。他強調之前因想自殺，已被安排會見心理和精神醫生16次，證實他無精神病。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跪地抱拳求保釋被拒<br />\n<br />\n法官林嘉欣指香港法律複雜，不宜沒有律師協助，「好好哋法援有大律師指派畀你唔使錢都唔要」。被告稱曾要求法援撤換大律師但被拒，故他寧可自己抗辯。被告又稱只是輕微打爛法官的枱面，故只承認刑毀，否認其餘兩罪，並解釋案發前一天替妻子買菜刀，放在袋內忘記了，而在庭上亮刀是因考慮過用刀割頸或割腕。<br />\n<br />\n控方指將傳召陳官和指模專家等6名證人，預留6天審訊，法官下令被告繼續還柙，被告聞言即哭喪着臉說：「不能再柙喇，再柙會柙死喇！」他在犯人欄內跪在地上抱拳請求法官批准保釋，但申請仍被拒。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCCC1163/17<br />\n■採訪蔡少玲、撰文黃幗慧  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n美報告：林鄭受京指使拒移交逃犯<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n劉小麗棄上訴部署補選　會否被二度DQ「要問林鄭聶德權」"},{"pid":"302931517499f8d3a65d4e3ef1ef4c0a3b904dae","tid":684333,"uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 Google下原來又係新移民<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦 支那 放晒D狗屎垃圾落黎<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171018/20186350\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171018%2F20186350&d=C5tuzVbK%2Fw0HjkR772TvCgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=41f7737b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171018%2F20186350&h=14c4b935\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171018/20186350</a>"},{"pid":"f779904c0f35b7875d99868e49c2134b10655403","tid":684333,"uid":163842,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:35:38.000Z","msg":"不能再柙喇，再柙會柙死喇！<br />\n<br />\n香港用哂d 法律資源陪呢班痴線佬癲"},{"pid":"0c11476e66c7766ac81c520eda2d312d1ae08263","tid":684333,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:37:47.000Z","msg":"人地講天在做人在看做乜屈人係人在做天在看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a361307628d84e0002657697abcf496264833e60","tid":684333,"uid":26953,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:41:32.000Z","msg":"天在做 人在看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6602dd90cc54650dd4ae31ec45d6736bcf4816ad","tid":684333,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:43:41.000Z","msg":"人在做 車在震"},{"pid":"748022b1bc9e812ae462a2c7046617159cada267","tid":684333,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"右面個善犬個樣咁&quot;拿&quot;型都做到警犬"},{"pid":"b1f62e4282e580f00d0c9d78774bdc4e10bf697c","tid":684333,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:45:18.000Z","msg":"又係講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d965129d406df2965d21d032b7777d248ca0b42","tid":684333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"呢排無人講熱錢流咁既 ?"},{"pid":"5a0971bcb086059b275e66e71b48cf2e1b8c1c69","tid":684333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d965129d406df2965d21d032b7777d248ca0b42","tid":684333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"呢排無人講熱錢流咁既 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"熱錢不再流動 ?"}]}